      <title>白俄罗斯称被定罪的德国人向总统请求赦免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/belarus-says-convicted-german-asked-president-for-pardon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[因代表乌克兰从事“雇佣军活动”而在白俄罗斯被判处死刑的德国公民里科·克里格 (Rico Krieger) 已请求白俄罗斯总统亚历山大·卢卡申科 (Alexander Lukashenko) 赦免他。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/belarus-says-convicted-german-asked-president-for-pardon</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 11:54:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
